eed 2<b>. Remove Varoma and set aside. Insert measuring cup and steam rice a further <b>5 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Season rice with salt and pepper and set aside to keep warm."},{"content":"Preheat oven broiler. Line a baking pan with foil and place pork on prepared pan, baste steamed pork tenderloins with reserved sauce and broil for 3-5 minutes. Slice Char Siu Pork, garnish with green onions and serve with steamed rice and remaining sauce."}],"basicInfo":["easy","5m","8h 40m","6 portions"]}